Document: AudioEffectEQ6  
Path: godot/classes/class_audioeffecteq6.rst  
Summary: AudioEffectEQ6 is a 6-band equalizer audio effect class in Godot.  

AudioEffectEQ6 is a class that provides a 6-band equalizer for audio processing. It allows adjusting the frequency bands to shape the audio output. The class inherits from AudioEffect, which is part of the AudioServer system. Key properties include frequency ranges for each band, gain values, and filter types. The effect can be applied to audio buses or nodes to modify sound characteristics. Implementation details involve configuring each band's parameters, such as center frequency, bandwidth, and gain. The class supports real-time adjustments and is used in audio mixing and mastering scenarios.
