Document: AudioEffectEQ6
Path: godot/classes/class_audioeffecteq6.rst
Summary: A 6-band equalizer audio effect allowing frequency modulation from 32 Hz to 10,000 Hz with adjustable gain per band.

Inherits: AudioEffectEQ < AudioEffect < Resource < RefCounted < Object
Adds a 6-band equalizer audio effect to an audio bus. Gives you control over frequencies from 32 Hz to 10000 Hz. Each frequency can be modulated between -60/+24 dB.
---CHUNK---
Document: AudioEffectEQ6
Path: godot/classes/class_audioeffecteq6.rst
Summary: AudioEffectEQ6 is an audio effect node with six adjustable frequency bands for equalization.

Frequency bands:
- Band 1 (32 Hz): Low-frequency bass control
- Band 2 (100 Hz): Sub-bass and low-end resonance
- Band 3 (320 Hz): Lower midrange frequencies
- Band 4 (1000 Hz): Midrange frequencies
- Band 5 (3200 Hz): Upper midrange and presence frequencies
- Band 6 (10000 Hz): High-frequency treble control

See also AudioEffectEQ, AudioEffectEQ10, AudioEffectEQ21.
---CHUNK---
